node.text: Alongside #TeamPanasonic, I’m already conquering my next challenge: helping to inspire a new generation of young people in the classroom. As a champion for education, my hope is to give kids the chance to pursue their passions.

node.text:
It was a joy to meet UNHCR Goodwill Ambassador and fellow Olympian @YusraMardini and hear her incredible story, from fleeing Syria all the way to her second Olympics with the @refugeeolympicteam!
See you at #Tokyo2020! @refugees
#StrongerTogether

node.text:
What a feeling when you dedicate yourself to a routine – from daily training to using water-activated @BICSoleil razors for the ultimate shave – and it pays off! Excited to be back home, taking some time to rest and reflect on the journey before attacking my next goals. ⁣
⁣
#BICSoleilPartner #BIC @bic_group

node.text: Alongside #TeamPanasonic, I’m already conquering my next challenge: helping to inspire a new generation of young people in the classroom. As a champion for education, my hope is to give kids the chance to pursue their passions.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Katie Ledecky on August 17, 2021 tagging @tyrsport, and @lydiaalicee_. May be an image of 1 person, swimming, riding a bicycle, indoor and pool.

node.text:
A little progression: when you hear the set ➡️ after the set 😂

These are some of the best feelings during workouts, and I’m grateful for 5 of the best training and racing weeks with @usaswimming. I also want to give a big thank you to @tyrsport for the support of my training, racing, and goals. Proud of what #TeamTYR accomplished this year, and I’m excited for what’s to come together 🙌🏼

📸- @mike2swim (also #grateful for you for capturing training camp memories to look back on for many years!)

Thanks @nyse for the honor of ringing the Closing Bell today, and thank you @empirestatebldg for having me light up the building last night (and for the incredible views)! 😍

📸: @nyse and @gettyimages
